00:23:43,079 --> 00:23:45,882
the record room for tests.

286
00:23:45,882 --> 00:23:48,518
Five minutes leftuntil the race begins.

287
00:23:48,518 --> 00:23:50,119
Did Ho-jin say he'll come?

