297
00:24:16,179 --> 00:24:17,981
Wow, you're really late.

298
00:24:17,981 --> 00:24:20,950
I'll go fast.

299
00:24:20,950 --> 00:24:23,620
It's the thirdKorea Motor Championship.

300
00:24:23,620 --> 00:24:27,957
1st place in the GT Class,Indigo's Kim Yi-soo.

301
00:24:27,957 --> 00:24:31,094
