303
00:24:35,131 --> 00:24:37,100
Fourth was Hwang Dae-jin.

304
00:24:37,100 --> 00:24:38,368
Feeling good, huh?

305
00:24:38,368 --> 00:24:40,570
- And don't pass upthe in course.- Okay.

