310
00:24:47,243 --> 00:24:50,246
Please clear awayfrom the grid.

311
00:24:50,246 --> 00:24:52,515
The sign board is up.

312
00:24:52,515 --> 00:25:37,660
Start your engines.

313
00:25:37,660 --> 00:25:40,630
