314
00:25:40,630 --> 00:25:43,266
Present lap time is 1:08:07.

315
00:25:43,266 --> 00:25:59,015
You're doing alright.

316
00:25:59,015 --> 00:26:00,950
Aren't you going too fast?

317
00:26:00,950 --> 00:26:02,752
I thought you were late.

318
00:26:02,752 --> 00:26:04,554
Right.

319
00:26:04,554 --> 00:26:05,555
Don't worry.

320
00:26:05,555 --> 00:26:17,734
I've been accident free for 10 years.Even as a speed taxi.

321
00:26:17,734 --> 00:26:43,860
It's the 7th head pin,so slow it down.

322
00:26:43,860 --> 00:26:51,167
He wants to kill himself!He's scaring me!

323
00:26:51,167 --> 00:26:53,503
The steering wheel is strange.I'm going in.

324
00:26:53,503 --> 00:27:02,512
Hurry up!

325
00:27:02,512 --> 00:27:03,279
What happened?

326
00:27:03,279 --> 00:27:04,580
The steering wheelshakes too much.

327
00:27:04,580 --> 00:27:05,448
Check the tires fast.

328
00:27:05,448 --> 00:27:06,649
Check the tires!

