00:27:28,004 --> 00:27:30,273
0.3 seconds behind in lap time.

332
00:27:30,273 --> 00:27:31,774
Run the courseinstead of placing.

333
00:27:31,774 --> 00:27:34,177
No, I have to place.

334
00:27:34,177 --> 00:27:52,995
You still have more to go,so it's okay. Be careful.

335
00:27:52,995 --> 00:27:57,900
The traffic lightsaren't cooperating today.

336
00:27:57,900 --> 00:28:00,937
Dae-jin, there's troubleon the course. Slow down!

337
00:28:00,937 --> 00:28:01,704
Dae-jin!

338
00:28:01,704 --> 00:28:05,608
What? What did you say?

339
00:28:05,608 --> 00:29:25,154
I can't hear you well.

340
00:29:25,154 --> 00:29:28,191
His pulse rate andbrain waves are improving,

341
00:29:28,191 --> 00:29:31,627
but he still can't wake up.It's too bad.

342
00:29:31,627 --> 00:29:34,797
Dr. Lee, what happenedto this patient?

343
00:29:34,797 --> 00:29:37,200
Didn't I tell you?

344
00:29:37,200 --> 00:29:40,469
Both brothers got intoa car accident.

345
00:29:40,469 --> 00:29:43,639
His older brother got hitby a truck while in a taxi.

346
00:29:43,639 --> 00:29:45,408
So he's pretty much dead.

347
00:29:45,408 --> 00:29:48,311
I guess so.

348
00:29:48,311 --> 00:29:49,745
But the younger one

349
00:29:49,745 --> 00:29:52,715
was in a car race accident.

350
00:29:52,715 --> 00:29:56,152
What a strange world.

351
00:29:56,152 --> 00:30:00,323
But is there any hopefor this patient?

352
00:30:00,323 --> 00:33:16,419
I don't know.

353
00:33:16,419 --> 00:33:17,520
Are you okay?

354
00:33:17,520 --> 00:33:21,223
Jung-woo, match the steps.You're falling back.

355
00:33:21,223 --> 00:33:27,196
You're supposed to turn there.

356
00:33:27,196 --> 00:33:29,398
Young-eun!

357
00:33:29,398 --> 00:33:40,910
Are you checkingthe distance? They're off.

358
00:33:40,910 --> 00:33:50,486
Mr. Kim, please check the lights.There are shadows onthe models' faces.

359
00:33:50,486 --> 00:33:58,227
Hello? Oh, hello.

360
00:33:58,227 --> 00:35:19,241
What?

361
00:35:19,241 --> 00:35:29,285
Please rest for now.

362
00:35:29,285 --> 00:36:24,106
It's really fortunate thatyou at least have come back.

363
00:36:24,106 --> 00:36:26,809
Are you okay?

364
00:36:26,809 --> 00:38:39,408
Get up.Go rest in your room.

365
00:38:39,408 --> 00:38:46,648
Hey, Dae-jin!

366
00:38:46,648 --> 00:38:49,551
Thanks for being alive.

367
00:38:49,551 --> 00:38:52,755
You were lying therelike a corpse,

368
00:38:52,755 --> 00:38:58,494
and I was helpless,thinking you'd leave forever.

369
00:38:58,494 --> 00:39:13,642
I'm just really happythat you're alive.

370
00:39:13,642 --> 00:39:21,950
You were a heavy smoker before.

371
00:39:21,950 --> 00:39:25,454
While you were in bed,know how stupid I acted?

372
00:39:25,454 --> 00:39:29,425
I went all the wayto the junkyard.

373
00:39:29,425 --> 00:39:35,297
I wanted to see your carget totally demolished.

374
00:39:35,297 --> 00:39:42,938
When I went to see it,I laughed a lot.

375
00:39:42,938 --> 00:39:46,308
You were in bed like that,

376
00:39:46,308 --> 00:39:49,478
and I was jealous of that car.

377
00:39:49,478 --> 00:39:54,016
I was acting overboard.

378
00:39:54,016 --> 00:40:01,390
But now

379
00:40:01,390 --> 00:40:35,657
I'm just really thankfulthat you've come back.

380
00:40:35,657 --> 00:40:36,692
Yae-joo.

381
00:40:36,692 --> 00:40:45,667
Hi, Eun-soo.Is Dae-jin really alright?

382
00:40:45,667 --> 00:40:47,035
Dae-jin.

383
00:40:47,035 --> 00:40:53,008
What are you doing?

384
00:40:53,008 --> 00:41:01,884
Have a seat.

385
00:41:01,884 --> 00:41:05,020
Did you buy that flower?

386
00:41:05,020 --> 00:41:13,028
No. I thought you bought it.

387
00:41:13,028 --> 00:41:16,064
Was Dae-jin always a good cook?

388
00:41:16,064 --> 00:41:32,114
The way he cutsvegetables is amazing.

389
00:41:32,114 --> 00:41:47,763
Sit. Yae-joo, too.

390
00:41:47,763 --> 00:41:49,998
Hurry and eat.

391
00:41:49,998 --> 00:41:51,500
Dae-jin.

392
00:41:51,500 --> 00:42:51,426
Right now, this is all thatI can do for you. Now eat.

393
00:42:51,426 --> 00:42:57,666
Dae-jin.

394
00:42:57,666 --> 00:43:18,320
Dae-jin...

395
00:43:18,320 --> 00:43:20,555
Mr. Hwang Dae-jin.

396
00:43:20,555 --> 00:43:25,560
- After you woke up...- My name is Hwang Ho-jin.

397
00:43:25,560 --> 00:43:32,067
Any other symptomsbesides headaches?

398
00:43:32,067 --> 00:43:46,515
Sometimes my ears ring.I'm cold. And I keep getting sleepy.

399
00:43:46,515 --> 00:43:51,286
But doctor, I'm Hwang Ho-jin.

400
00:43:51,286 --> 00:43:54,656
What happened to me?

401
00:43:54,656 --> 00:43:59,761
From a psychologist's perspective,his depression and hysteria

402
00:43:59,761 --> 00:44:02,964
have sprung up in a peculiarway after his trauma.

403
00:44:02,964 --> 00:44:05,434
On the surface,

404
00:44:05,434 --> 00:44:08,036
he believes he's Hwang Ho-jin.

405
00:44:08,036 --> 00:44:13,008
But the problem isthat his consciousness firmly

406
00:44:13,008 --> 00:44:16,912
believes that he's possessed.

407
00:44:16,912 --> 00:44:18,780
Possessed?

408
00:44:18,780 --> 00:44:26,388
If I explain it simply, the body istaken over by someone else's spirit.

409
00:44:26,388 --> 00:44:32,360
The best way to know is to findproof of his believe fromhis unconscious.

410
00:44:32,360 --> 00:44:47,976
Doctor. How can this be possible?

411
00:44:47,976 --> 00:44:49,911
Oh my goodness.Oh my goodness.

412
00:44:49,911 --> 00:44:51,379
Your hand.

413
00:44:51,379 --> 00:44:55,050
Oh no.

414
00:44:55,050 --> 00:44:57,352
Eun-soo, he cut his hand.

415
00:44:57,352 --> 00:44:58,954
He kept saying he's Ho-jin.

416
00:44:58,954 --> 00:45:01,256
Wait.

417
00:45:01,256 --> 00:45:05,060
My hands aren't listening to me.

418
00:45:05,060 --> 00:45:06,795
I don't know how this happened.

419
00:45:06,795 --> 00:45:08,830
Dae-jin, hurry and go inside first.

420
00:45:08,830 --> 00:45:10,532
Yeah, let's hurry, Dae-jin.

421
00:45:10,532 --> 00:45:15,871
I'm not Dae-jin.

422
00:45:15,871 --> 00:45:20,275
I don't know. I don't knowwhy I'm like this.

423
00:45:20,275 --> 00:45:26,681
Hey. Pull yourself together.You're Hwang Dae-jin.

424
00:45:26,681 --> 00:45:36,424
You're the Hwang Dae-jin.I've always liked!

425
00:45:36,424 --> 00:45:47,369
Eun-soo, I'm sorry.I'm really sorry.

426
00:45:47,369 --> 00:46:01,316
Yae-joo. Dae-jin is still sick.

427
00:46:01,316 --> 00:46:05,687
He's doing this becausehe's still mentally unstable.

428
00:46:05,687 --> 00:46:09,925
When time passes, he'll be better.

429
00:46:09,925 --> 00:46:17,732
That bastard. He's trying tosuck me dry forever.

430
00:46:17,732 --> 00:46:30,412
I'll be backafter I give this to him.

431
00:46:30,412 --> 00:46:44,226
The gift yourfather gave you.

432
00:46:44,226 --> 00:47:24,099
I've finally fixed it.

433
00:47:24,099 --> 00:47:28,770
- Can you hear my voice?- Yes.

434
00:47:28,770 --> 00:47:32,007
Tell me your name.

435
00:47:32,007 --> 00:47:33,909
Hwang Ho-jin.

436
00:47:33,909 --> 00:47:35,543
Good.

437
00:47:35,543 --> 00:47:40,916
You're falling into acalmer and deeper sleep.

438
00:47:40,916 --> 00:47:44,386
Imagine a cloud.

439
00:47:44,386 --> 00:47:49,791
A soft wind is blowing.The cloud is moving slowly.

440
00:47:49,791 --> 00:47:53,995
Very slowly.

441
00:47:53,995 --> 00:48:05,106
Now look slowlybelow the cloud.

442
00:48:05,106 --> 00:48:10,178
What do you see?

443
00:48:10,178 --> 00:48:12,047
A road.

444
00:48:12,047 --> 00:48:20,488
What's on top of this road?

445
00:48:20,488 --> 00:48:23,625
A taxi. Taxi.

446
00:48:23,625 --> 00:48:32,300
Are you riding in this taxi?

447
00:48:32,300 --> 00:48:33,468
I don't know.

448
00:48:33,468 --> 00:48:39,574
You're moving forward.Slowly.

449
00:48:39,574 --> 00:48:49,851
What do you seein front of you?

450
00:48:49,851 --> 00:48:58,093
What do you see?

451
00:48:58,093 --> 00:49:08,937
Calm down.Put your mind at ease.

452
00:49:08,937 --> 00:49:11,940
Common symptomsfor possessed patients

453
00:49:11,940 --> 00:49:15,844
are a drop in their temperatureand feeling very cold.

454
00:49:15,844 --> 00:49:20,215
They keep sleeping,and even their ears ring.

455
00:49:20,215 --> 00:49:27,522
But doctor how couldmy husband's soul...

456
00:49:27,522 --> 00:49:32,494
Even modern psychology can't provewhether possession exists or not.

457
00:49:32,494 --> 00:49:52,247
By simply acknowledging itand nursing him is better.

458
00:49:52,247 --> 00:50:04,559
Take your medicine.

459
00:50:04,559 --> 00:50:12,000
How I'm acting now...I'm not sick, Eun-soo.

460
00:50:12,000 --> 00:52:10,685
I understand. But you have totake this medicine.

461
00:52:10,685 --> 00:52:13,521
Eun-soo.

462
00:52:13,521 --> 00:52:20,061
Eun-soo, open the door.

463
00:52:20,061 --> 00:52:23,631
Eun-soo, open the door.

464
00:52:23,631 --> 00:52:29,070
I'm not going to do anything.

465
00:52:29,070 --> 00:52:38,913
Eun-soo.

466
00:52:38,913 --> 00:52:50,825
I'm sorry.I didn't want to do this.

467
00:52:50,825 --> 00:53:37,405
But being alone in that roomis too hard for me.

468
00:53:37,405 --> 00:53:43,711
Don't go.

469
00:53:43,711 --> 00:53:50,084
I'm scared, Eun-soo.

470
00:53:50,084 --> 00:54:00,762
If I sleep in that room alone,I feel like I'll never wake up.

471
00:54:00,762 --> 00:54:22,583
I'm very frightened.

472
00:54:22,583 --> 00:54:32,093
Being with Dae-jinis too hard on me.

473
00:54:32,093 --> 00:54:42,637
I feel like I'm unconsciouslylooking for Ho-jin in him.

474
00:54:42,637 --> 00:54:56,217
No. Honestly, I saw him.

475
00:54:56,217 --> 00:55:01,823
I'm so confused.

476
00:55:01,823 --> 00:55:09,430
I feel like I know whatyou're going through.

477
00:55:09,430 --> 00:55:16,070
Eun-soo. I finished my thesis,so I have a lot of time now.

478
00:55:16,070 --> 00:55:23,811
If it's okay that I spend timewith him, he'll get better.

479
00:55:23,811 --> 00:55:26,881
When you were in the marines,

480
00:55:26,881 --> 00:55:29,650
you said it was hell,but you felt peaceful.

481
00:55:29,650 --> 00:55:32,387
If we work our butt offat my family's ranch,

482
00:55:32,387 --> 00:55:36,391
that mildew in your headwill wash away.

483
00:55:36,391 --> 00:55:41,295
Yae-joo. Where can I go?

484
00:55:41,295 --> 00:55:47,101
I'm not going anywhere.This is my place.

485
00:55:47,101 --> 00:55:52,106
Eun-soo agreed with me.

486
00:55:52,106 --> 00:55:54,041
Eun-soo did?

487
00:55:54,041 --> 00:56:02,817
Yes, your sister-in-law.

488
00:56:02,817 --> 00:56:07,588
If I just stay here like this,

489
00:56:07,588 --> 00:56:12,360
everything will turn back to normal.

490
00:56:12,360 --> 00:56:15,830
Hey, how long will you keep this up?

491
00:56:15,830 --> 00:56:18,099
Are you planningto drive us crazy?

492
00:56:18,099 --> 00:56:21,836
Eun-soo is having it hardenough taking care of Ho-jin.

493
00:56:21,836 --> 00:56:32,213
Seeing him in a coma forover a year is hell enough.

494
00:56:32,213 --> 00:58:15,917
What did you just say?

495
00:58:15,917 --> 00:58:21,756
Look. Look very carefully.

496
00:58:21,756 --> 00:58:37,104
That's Hwang Dae-jin's face.Know do you get it? Do you?

497
00:58:37,104 --> 00:58:48,182
If it's that hard on you,I'll become Dae-jin.

498
00:58:48,182 --> 00:59:11,472
I'll live like Dae-jin.

499
00:59:11,472 --> 00:59:16,577
Scared, huh? Cutting grass,chasing and milking cows.

500
00:59:16,577 --> 00:59:19,480
You'll probably pass out.

501
00:59:19,480 --> 00:59:39,166
But don't worry. I'll help you.

502
00:59:39,166 --> 00:59:53,414
Ho-jin. It's Eun-soo.I see that my Ho-jin is still sleeping.

503
00:59:53,414 --> 01:00:03,324
I thought you hated being lazy.So how could yousleep this long?

504
01:00:03,324 --> 01:00:09,997
I've changed a lot lately.

505
01:00:09,997 --> 01:00:17,672
I get angry with people a lot,and I don't laugh easily.

506
01:00:17,672 --> 01:00:24,345
If you saw me,you'd be surprised.

507
01:00:24,345 --> 01:00:37,692
I can't remember your voice.

508
01:00:37,692 --> 01:00:47,435
The harder I try, the moreI can't remember.

509
01:00:47,435 --> 01:00:56,577
I wish you'd call me just once.

510
01:00:56,577 --> 01:01:05,453
Eun-soo. Hey, Eun-soo.

511
01:01:05,453 --> 01:01:40,721
Without you, I can't do anything.

512
01:01:40,721 --> 01:01:44,525
Go!

513
01:01:44,525 --> 01:01:47,995
Hey. You're working upa real sweat.

514
01:01:47,995 --> 01:01:51,365
Trying hard to make my family rich?

515
01:01:51,365 --> 01:01:52,900
Dae-jin.

516
01:01:52,900 --> 01:03:36,737
Leave me alone if you want tomake me into Dae-jin.

517
01:03:36,737 --> 01:03:46,947
Since you're not complainingand whining, you're no fun at all.

518
01:03:46,947 --> 01:03:54,722
Fine. I guess I'll just bea one-woman band forever.

519
01:03:54,722 --> 01:04:04,164
I'll play drums with yousometimes. Bang, bang.

520
01:04:04,164 --> 01:04:12,640
Hey. Like you,

521
01:04:12,640 --> 01:04:17,912
if I could become someone else,

522
01:04:17,912 --> 01:04:27,688
then I wish I had never met you.

523
01:04:27,688 --> 01:04:38,666
Then I could've madeabout 100 guys like me.

524
01:04:38,666 --> 01:04:40,434
Hey.

525
01:04:40,434 --> 01:04:47,841
Look. When you do this,you're totally Dae-jin.

526
01:04:47,841 --> 01:04:52,046
Now you laugh for me?

527
01:04:52,046 --> 01:05:52,439
I tried so hard to see it just once.

528
01:05:52,439 --> 01:05:58,612
Hey. I don't care who you are.

529
01:05:58,612 --> 01:06:00,814
You're simplysomeone who I love.

530
01:06:00,814 --> 01:08:56,590
Also, I'm going to hold onto that love. Until I die.

531
01:08:56,590 --> 01:09:09,970
I'm sorry. I had no choicebut to come back.

532
01:09:09,970 --> 01:09:14,641
For Eskimos,

533
01:09:14,641 --> 01:09:18,412
when someone they love dies,

534
01:09:18,412 --> 01:09:22,449
they gather and talk aboutthat person for five days.

535
01:09:22,449 --> 01:09:28,655
While they talk, they erase theirmemories of that person.

536
01:09:28,655 --> 01:09:34,995
Afterwards, they nevertalk about that person again.

537
01:09:34,995 --> 01:09:43,837
If they do, then that person's soulcan't rest in peace.

538
01:09:43,837 --> 01:09:45,939
Let's talk about Ho-jin.

